&lt;h2 id=&quot;results&quot;&gt;Results &lt;a class=&quot;w-headline-link&quot; href=&quot;https://web.dev/yahoo-japan-news/#results&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
